            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Add module support for Zend_Translate similar to this solution:\r\nhttp:\/\/blog.vandenbos.org\/2009\/07\/09\/zend-framework-per-module-translation-sources\/\r\n\r\nEvery module has its own language dir, e.g.: application\/modules\/user\/lang\r\nThe translations have to be ADDED to (not replace) the Zend_Translate-Instance and stored in Registry with the default 'Zend_Translate'-key"
